
The design thinking assignment has taught me to be more empathetic in understanding problems in order 
to come up with a well constructed solution. As a way to improve my potential in the industry, 
I need to be consistent in improving my way of viewing things and problems, preferably by following the Design Thinking
phases because it is able to help me make a thorough and comprehensive plan to successfully solve a problem. 
Consequently, I will be able to produce a well planned solution for my problem.
